\sum_{k=2}^{n+1} \left( \frac{k-1}{n} \prod_{i=1}^{k-2} \left(1-\frac{i}{n}\right) \right)
\sum_{k=2}^{n+1} \frac{k-1}{n^{k-1}} \frac{(n-1)!}{(n-k+1)!}
 \displaystyle\prod_{i=1}^{0} \left(1-\frac{i}{n}\right)=1 
\def\frc{\displaystyle\frac} a_1:=\frc1n
b_1:=\frc{n-1}n
b_2
a_3:=b_2\cdot\frc3n
b_3:=b_2\cdot\frc{n-3}n
b_n=0
a_1+a_2+\dots+a_n=1\,.
